"{\"uid\": \"thetablet.org-paris-olympic-committee-makes-soft-apology-for-last-supper-drag-parody\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Elise Ann Allen ROME (Crux) - Representatives of the Paris 2024 Olympics Committee have apologized to anyone offended by a drag parody of the Last Supper during the opening ceremony, insisting that their intention was to foster inclusion and celebrate diversity.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"score\": 0.9999999758160815, \"rank\": 2.4183871678946255e-08, \"text\": \"Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Crux\", \"from\": 24, \"to\": 29}, {\"ngram\": \"Representatives\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics Committee\", \"from\": 52, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 105, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"a drag parody\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 137}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 156}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 184}, {\"ngram\": \"their intention\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 240}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps was asked about the outcry during an International Olympic Committee news conference Sunday, saying in response, \\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\\\"\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.214857437949346e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the outcry\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"response\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" she said, adding, \\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"the polls\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense, we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly, the ceremony's artistic director, in his own remarks to theAssociated Pressabout the event, said it was meant to celebrate diversity and pay tribute to feasting and French gastronomy.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999993153867378, \"rank\": 6.84323859019513e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's artistic director\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"his own remarks\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"theAssociated Pressabout\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock,\\\" he said, saying, \\\"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The apology was made in response to a wave of backlash from Catholics, members of other Christian communities, atheists, and members of other faith groups to the July 26 opening ceremony for the Paris Olympics, which featured a group of scantily clad men in drag dancing provocatively while parodying the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1223, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.297332701801895e-16, \"