://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9993840963939215, \"rank\": 0.0006132836674941719, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some commentators\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"the wake\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversy\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"the feast\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"a nod\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the artists who participated in the parody have confirmed in online social media posts and in comments to the press that the performance was, in fact, intended to imitate Leonardo da Vinci's famed painting of the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2401, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6859705879503314e-28, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the artists\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"the parody\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"online social media posts\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"the press\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French drag queen and rapper Piche from the show Drag Race France spoke to French media, saying the intention was to create a tableau of the Last Supper in the pouring rain.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2457, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999993153867378, \"rank\": 6.84323859019513e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Drag Race France\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drag_Race_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2532, \"end\": 2538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999993153867378, \"rank\": 6.84323859019513e-07, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rapper Piche\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"the intention\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"a tableau\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"the pouring rain\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I received a lot of messages of support and people who were very happy that I was there and very surprised that there were drag queens at the opening ceremony,\\\" he said, adding that the opposition to the performance indicates that \\\"we have succeeded and we have done what had to be done, that we have been fair and representative.\\\"\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"messages\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposition\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 2833, \"to\": 2848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Art always divides.\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Art\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as it does not move people, it's not art for me,\\\" he said, saying the depiction of the Last Supper \\\"is not a provocation.\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"the depiction\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3074}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"a provocation\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a biblical representation that has been reused in pop culture for decades and it's never really been a problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a biblical representation\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"pop culture\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 3188, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were no real provocations or anything that was truly obscene.\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no real provocations\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3268}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We did not make fun of the painting at all \\u2026 it's really just because it's queers and drag queens who use that representation that it bothers,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"the painting\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3340}, {\"ngram\": \"queers\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3402}, {\"ngram\": \"that representation\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, Barbara Butch, a lesbian who donned a silver headdress and low-cut dress while portraying the figure of Jesus in the Last Supper parody, said the opening ceremony was intended to bring people together.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3470, \"end\": 3483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}, {\"begin\": 3574, \"end\": 3579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999997644409, \"rank\": 2.3559296506354007e-10, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lesbian\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver headdress and low-cut dress\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3542}, {\"ngram\": \"the figure\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper parody\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3605}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to her Instagram profile, Butch is \\\"a Love activist, DJ and producer based in Paris.\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3690, \"end\": 3699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\