logy\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In fact, it's kind of a masterpiece of woke duplicity \\u2026 If they felt this is meant to mollify Christians, I would think again,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4839, \"end\": 4849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9723672467228136, \"rank\": 0.028085276990019867, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 4748, \"to\": 4752}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of a masterpiece\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4780}, {\"ngram\": \"woke duplicity\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pointing to Descamps's assertion that they did not intend to offend any religious group, Bishop Barron said, \\\"Give me a break.\\\"\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 5010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4895, \"end\": 4903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 4972, \"end\": 4978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9998763467333729, \"rank\": 0.0001236685585754081, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 4979, \"end\": 4985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.462700256646377e-19, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4970}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 5001, \"to\": 5008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a group of drag queens cavorting in a sexually provocative way, clearly in imitation of Da Vinci's Last Supper, which presents to the world the Last Supper of Jesus, and no disrespect was meant?\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5109, \"end\": 5117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.926333653570847e-32, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 5180, \"end\": 5185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999997644409, \"rank\": 2.3559296506354007e-10, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 5021, \"to\": 5028}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5043}, {\"ngram\": \"a sexually provocative way\", \"from\": 5057, \"to\": 5083}, {\"ngram\": \"imitation\", \"from\": 5096, \"to\": 5105}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5151, \"to\": 5160}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 5161, \"to\": 5176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you think anyone takes that seriously?\\\"\", \"from\": 5216, \"to\": 5258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 5229, \"to\": 5235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"he said.\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also took issue with the statement that the intention was to celebrate community and tolerance, saying there is tolerance \\\"except for those pesky 2.6 billion Christians on the planet.\\\"\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5430, \"end\": 5440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9723672467228136, \"rank\": 0.028085276990019867, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"issue\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 5293, \"to\": 5306}, {\"ngram\": \"the intention\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5325}, {\"ngram\": \"community\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5366}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 5384, \"to\": 5393}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 5444, \"to\": 5454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone's welcome, everyone's tolerated, all this lovely diversity, until you get to anyone that disagrees with your ideology, like these 2.6 billion people.\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5487}, {\"ngram\": \"all this lovely diversity\", \"from\": 5501, \"to\": 5526}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 5545, \"to\": 5551}, {\"ngram\": \"your ideology\", \"from\": 5572, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"these 2.6 billion people\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So do not give me this business about tolerance and diversity,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 5618, \"to\": 5690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this business\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5649}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5665}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Referring to Descamps's statement that their goal of celebrating tolerance was achieved, Bishop Barron asked rhetorically, \\\"I wonder what planet they are living on if they think that harmony and peace and all this was achieved by this clear affront to Christians.\\\"\", \"from\": 5692, \"to\": 5956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5705, \"end\": 5713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 5781, \"end\": 5787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.9998763467333729, \"rank\": 0.0001236685585754081, \"text\": \"Bishop\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 5788, \"end\": 5794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.462700256646377e-19, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 5944, \"end\": 5954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9723672467228136, \"rank\": 0.028085276990019867, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their goal\", \"from\": 5731, \"to\": 5741}, {\"ngram\": \"tolerance\", \"from\": 5757, \"to\": 5766}, {\"ngram\": \"what planet\", \"from\": 5825, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"harmony\", \"from\": 5875, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"peace\", \"from\": 5887, \"to\": 5892}, {\"ngram\": \"this clear affront\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 5940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bishop Barron also condemned the wording of the apology as condescending, saying the tone does not read apologetic, but rather says, \\\"If you are so simple-minded and stupid to have been offended by this wonderful expression of French culture, well, we are sorry about that.\\\"\", \"from\": 5958, \"to\": 6232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5958, \"end\": 5964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishop\", \"score\": 0.999876346733