g remark\", \"from\": 6358, \"to\": 6383}, {\"ngram\": \"any bad feelings\", \"from\": 6406, \"to\": 6422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This apology will do little to satisfy Christians who were offended by the performance, he said, saying, \\\"A real apology would be something like, 'this was a mistake, it should never have been done, we are sorry for it.'\\\"\", \"from\": 6469, \"to\": 6690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6508, \"end\": 6518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9723672467228136, \"rank\": 0.028085276990019867, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This apology\", \"from\": 6469, \"to\": 6481}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 6540, \"to\": 6555}, {\"ngram\": \"A real apology\", \"from\": 6575, \"to\": 6589}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 6599, \"to\": 6608}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 6625, \"to\": 6634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think Christians should be mollified, I think we should keep raising our voices,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6692, \"to\": 6792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6708, \"end\": 6718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9723672467228136, \"rank\": 0.028085276990019867, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our voices\", \"from\": 6771, \"to\": 6781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Username or Email Password Remember Me Your email will be used to send you The Tablet newsletter.\", \"from\": 6794, \"to\": 6902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6880, \"end\": 6890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Tablet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.098874987013776e-46, \"text\": \"The Tablet\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wik